{"tid":1632113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向被裝修商店提出不再裝修條件","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:08:47.000Z","uid":61886,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e53dd2fcbbc3391a3b1ef8cb2453f5ac489bde9d","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"個人意見<br />\n<br />\n我哋做每一樣野都有我哋嘅訴求同原因<br />\n如果商戶可以達成我哋嘅要求<br />\n我哋可以停止裝修<br />\n<br />\n就好似如果政府達成五大訴求<br />\n我哋就唔會繼續示威一樣<br />\n<br />\n依個係比黨鐵既條件<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WFMNuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WFMNuk.jpg&h=ffd58ad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n做到晒依四樣<br />\n我哋會停止裝修黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n至於比咩條件比美心、360、吉野家、中資企業<br />\n我地可以討論一下<br />\n<br />\n一係達成我哋嘅要求<br />\n一係繼續裝修"},{"pid":"fbf13c43920a308b494db94cd25c0a15afb1a58a","tid":1632113,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3a893713547651bd5a51349b44a408da158fa79","tid":1632113,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"agger <br />\n令互屌post沉底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[長文][召喚全世界] 嘈完就入黎 睇下下一步應該做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9a04e972b47193b13babfc0496738b26474f3b93","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"當我地有提出條件<br />\n對方唔答應<br />\n我哋裝修更加出師有名"},{"pid":"0e9d20b1031ba1b140e89956a8803709ef940863","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"無止境冇訴求嘅裝修<br />\n只會令我哋形象變差"},{"pid":"a9f6d4b98cc8acf8dc3a9a8dd116068fe15c1701","tid":1632113,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"交人 賠償 捐款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830c8cac67117ddc4a921ece28ef3533686e9aed","tid":1632113,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzE523y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzE523y.jpg&h=1a0e2ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKw4zaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKw4zaf.jpg&h=43348a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pr7jn3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpr7jn3B.jpg&h=0499d221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"448d1ee5b90cea8b1be6963ca405fc4dc18143f2","tid":1632113,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:58.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d41c06595afc35afabf34d1c4281868b61a61e94","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"推有用post"},{"pid":"4446f8050f8087d9c339f57edf4daf95f3b1a48c","tid":1632113,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ccb208df9397f3c2c1da868866d5e836ae5da5c","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9f6d4b98cc8acf8dc3a9a8dd116068fe15c1701","tid":1632113,"uid":57566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"交人 賠償 捐款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:40.000Z","msg":"例如美心<br />\n佢地無人交啦<br />\n咁有無咩其他條件<br />\n例如捐錢比星火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a440ede3c82c197eff490da6bbb4d168eb9669e8","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39e68ba990006f77808a89ec036fef3cf0acae88","tid":1632113,"uid":299476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"依個好踩界，算唔算恐嚇？有預謀？<br />\n定係協持人質去談判？<br />\n<br />\nUmm...唔好用提出不再裝修條件咁威逼既語氣...<br />\n試下利誘？<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 黨鐵最大股東唔係政府咩？想斷佢運兵線、補給線、犬隻衞星休息站？<br />\n仲有，依頭先講完觀塘站係班狗自己裝修，你做咩攬曬上身。"},{"pid":"173f9c27c26900941a14d71ee88e47728b260d47","tid":1632113,"uid":28485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:14.000Z","msg":"美心其實始作俑者係太子女<br />\n但佢地早就同太子女割左蓆<br />\n叫太子女道歉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de4b308606a996f6493a35c58e661b3a0cbebfc","tid":1632113,"uid":42691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"非常好"},{"pid":"9f4683ea62b73e0cbaec27c64446c254da5837c6","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39e68ba990006f77808a89ec036fef3cf0acae88","tid":1632113,"uid":299476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:09:49.000Z","msg":"依個好踩界，算唔算恐嚇？有預謀？<br />\n定係協持人質去談判？<br />\n<br />\nUmm...唔好用提出不再裝修條件咁威逼既語氣...<br />\n試下利誘？<br />\n<br />\nBTW, 黨鐵最大股東唔係政府咩？想斷佢運兵線、補給線、犬隻衞星休息站？<br />\n仲有，依頭先講完觀塘站係班狗自己裝修，你做咩攬曬上身。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"1. 咁五大訴求係咪威迫？<br />\n2. 唔計火燒觀塘站，其他係咪手足爆先"},{"pid":"1e4fd0f3d46c00d5c8fd146d1518de861fc89667","tid":1632113,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"1630978f8d2d31e61875b01b72885a0be31c8cc6","tid":1632113,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"其實無論點都等人權法過左再接JOB做工程<br />\n唔好為左出氣而失去左真正既勝利<br />\n你裝修佢幾多間鋪都抵唔上個集團被人制裁"},{"pid":"943383c2cf00bb4e144e23b8766f45931c906e61","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e73b75a71a9ab2720bda601bcf601d5b9acbcf0a","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"140e3c3c195771b3ffcf3037bdaeafb30ba014a3","tid":1632113,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f5cfb2d6ca0336eb02e522c7a3f46dae121ae77","tid":1632113,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:08:11.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 黨鐵100%政府control"},{"pid":"335d86a4a272d0357610cf12fee489602c1fef8e","tid":1632113,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:08:47.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n麻煩幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}